label("C", C, SW);

label("3000 km", (A+C)/2, S);

label("3250 km", (A+B)/2, NE);

draw((0,125)--(125,125)--(125,0));

[/asy]

Piravena chose the least expensive way to travel between cities.  What was the total cost?

